sub_title: Helpt CEO's/VP's/Sales/Start-ups/Scale-ups meer afspraken in de agenda te krijgen met de juiste mensen bij de juiste bedrijven.
summary:
Thank you for visiting my Linkedin profile. My name is Debbie Hannis, Recruitment Consultant at Venderion Working Abroad B.V. We support European software developers that want to relocate to the Netherlands.

Venderion has an active network of >500 software companies in the Netherlands that develop innovative products and services. Currently we have a lot of exciting positions available ranging from web, (native) mobile, middleware and embedded developers. 

What you can expect as a candidate:
- receive job offers that fit your profile
- guidance throughout the whole selection process
- support with relocation: housing and the necessary administrative issues
- you'll be hired directly by the software developing company (so not by Venderion)
- employment is intended to be long term 

Are you interested?
Feel free to get in touch with me via Linkedin or send me a mail: debbie.hannis@venderion.nl

And if you know anyone else that might be interested, maybe some of your friends, colleagues or a former classmate, I'm happy to get to know them as well.

Looking forward to hearing from you!
Debbie
